reviewText: This is one of the best sermons I have ever heard!  Ken Davis makes an excellent point, while entertaining the audience and keeping us laughing!  I have shared this with all of my coworkers and non-christian friends and have had wonderful feedback.  What a great way to share God's truth with our neighbors!

THIS KEN DAVIS RECORDING IS ALTOGETHER UPLIFTING, ENCOURAGING, PROVACATIVE, HILARIOUS, POIGNANT, AND WORTHY TO BE WATCHED OVER AND OVER AGAIN.  I HAVE WATCHED IT MANY TIMES WITH MY CHILDREN, HUSBAND, AND BIBLE STUDY GROUP.

I bought this and one other Ken Davis video to show to my high school sunday school class. (That way they get a break from me!) I like his humor and the way he relates scriptural events to our lives. Good for high school age through adult. I recommend it.

NOT HIS TRADITIONAL "STAND UP" - THIS WAS FROM AN APPEARANCE OF HIS AT A CHURCH IN SAN DIEGO - PACKED FULL OF STUFF TO MAKE A PERSON THINK AND REALIZE THAT IT'S OKAY TO BE A SHEEP - AS LONG AS YOU HAVE THE RIGHT SHEPHERD!

You can never go wrong with a Ken Davis movie! This is one of our family favorites. :)

If you are looking for good, CLEAN humor, this is it.  Ken Davis' way of telling stories from his own life makes them even funnier. This video also has inspiriation for those who may be feeling like lost sheep. I would recommend this seller. Good quality product & timely shipping.

My church has shown short clips of Mr. Davis and we have ordered several of his DVD's and watch them again and again.  They are also a great gift for Sunday School teachers, Pastors, friends, parents, anyone who loves to laugh and loves the Lord!
I have the cd of this, so to see it put a new spin on it. Ken is a great story teller and teacher. I recommend this video to all who want to laugh. Find out what the "really big boo" is all about!
this is awesome, LOVE LOVE LOVE Ken Davis - his honest outlook on life and spirituality is refreshing. highly recommend!
i had a great buying experiance with this company it arrived on time and they are very good i would recomend them to everyone i know
I loved the DVD. It is funny and my kid and I enjoyed it very much. Would recommend it to anyone.
Shipper was good.  Story line was great, solid Christian entertainment.  Very funny with good moral to the story.  Would buy more from Ken Davis.
Very thought provoking, with the right balance of humor and a great message. I had wanted to see one of Ken Davis's tapes for a long time, and was not disappointed.
This talk is as funny and meaningful as it was when I first heard Ken Davis in the 1970s or 1980s.
If you want to help people learn about our Lord and Savior, this is the one! This will bring people to the Lord along with sidesplitting laughter.. :)

This Ken Davis DVD was received very quickly and in perfect condition.  I am very pleased with the sender and the purchase.

The DVD is full of humor and a powerful spiritual message as well.  I recommend it very highly!
Great video!  Ken Davis gives an excellent message with his great sense of humor.  With incredible humor he helps remind us how we are so much like sheep...in need of the Shepherd.
super sheep is wonderful. love the analogy about a sports team named "the sheep" and "what would the cheerleaders say?" LOL LOL this is a great CD.
Ken Davis at his finest. Great video
Love Ken Davis!  he's so much fun!

This is so funny I laughed until I cried in a few spots. It's a brilliant take on the "sheep and shepherd" idea. We just take it for granted that it's cool to be His sheep. I had no idea sheep were so dumb and geeky (in Davis' words). Makes some very good points.
Though some of his jokes are repeats, they serve as a good reminder of the message.
Really loved this DVD.  It is a solid Christian message laced with humor that is very relatable in our human frailty.
Love Ken Davis.  He is hilarious and profound!
Ken Davis is one of our favorite Christian speakers/entertainers.  Would recommend this to everyone.  Funny - yet very significant in our world today.
